Renovalia Energy, First Reserve Agree to Create Renewable-Power Venture

-- B y   T o d d   W h i t e
-- 
2011-12-05T08:31:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-05/renovalia-energy-first-reserve-agree-to-create-renewable-power-venture.html
Renovalia Energy, a Spanish developer
of renewable-energy projects, formed a joint venture with U.S.
private equity firm First Reserve Corp. to own and operate wind
farms in  Europe  and North America, they said today in a joint
statement. First Reserve has committed $150 million to the
business, they said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Todd White at 
 twhite2@bloomberg.net  